Class DataTransportImplFile

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CODAStateMachine, StatedObject, DataTransport

    public class DataTransportImplFile
extends DataTransportAdapter
    Implement a DataTransport that uses DataChannels based on EVIO format files. This class does nothing besides provide a way to create file channels which do all the work.
    Author:
    heyes Date: Nov 10, 2008

        This method creates a DataChannel object.
        Parameters:
        name - name of DataChannel
        attributeMap - hashmap of attributes taken from XML config file
        isInput - true if this channel puts data into the Emu, else false
        emu - Emu owning this transport
